    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Large rectangular pans without lids, slightly deeper than baking pans, intended for roasting meat and poultry in an oven. For enamel pans with lids, use "roasters (cookware)."</Note_Text>
